## Examples

### Mermaid Flowchart
```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Decision}
    B -->|Yes| C[Process A]
    B -->|No| D[Process B]
    C --> E[End]
    D --> E
```

### PlantUML Class Diagram
```plantuml
@startuml
class Animal {
  +String name
  +int age
  +makeSound()
}
class Dog {
  +String breed
  +bark()
}
Animal <|-- Dog
@enduml
```

### Graphviz DOT Diagram
```dot
digraph G {
    A -> B;
    B -> C;
    C -> A;
}
```
